= ltib configuration process =

 * choose a board
  * list must be auto-generated

 * choose linux kernel (2.0/2.4/2.6)

 * choose clibrary
  * This implies the toolchain

 * choose distribution (uclinux, custom, fedora) ?

 * choose device profile (e.g minimal/maximal/accespoint/firewall/nas)

 * choose packages
  * (re)build
  * install


